{"_path":"/china/fujian/xiamen","_dir":"fujian","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_empty":false,"title":"厦门","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"厦门"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"厦门"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"游玩"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"游玩"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"list","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鼓浪屿"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海上冲浪"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"美食"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美食"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"游记"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"游记"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当日晚上到达，入住双子塔。夜游沙坡尾，路遇很多美女。厦大因疫情，无法进入。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"次日乘船游鼓浪屿。 竟然看到了很多学校，这些学生难道坐船来读书？很神奇。美好的沙滩，海水。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三日，开船去眺望金门。坐船头真的很刺激，海水真的非常咸。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"四日返程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"计划参考"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"计划参考"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"D1"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南普陀寺(2小时) → 厦门大学(3小时) → 芙蓉隧道(30分钟) → 厦大白城沙滩(30分钟) → 厦门环岛路(1小时) → 胡里山炮台(1小时) → 曾厝垵(2小时)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"D2"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"厦门园林植物园(2~5小时) → 沙坡尾(3小时) → 世茂云上厦门观光厅(1小时) → 中山路步行街(3小时)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"D3"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鼓浪屿风琴博物馆(1小时) → 厦门市鼓浪屿风景名胜区-三一堂(30分钟) → 日光岩(鼓浪屿)(1小时) → 菽庄花园(2小时) → 鼓浪屿钢琴博物馆(20分钟) → 皓月园(30分钟) → 龙头路商业街(2小时)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tips"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每年8月前后，是台风多发季节，此时前往厦门一定要多关注气象信息。由于台风的影响，航班可能会取消，沿海的一些景点可能会关闭，因此需要避开台风季"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"游玩","depth":2,"text":"游玩"},{"id":"美食","depth":2,"text":"美食"},{"id":"游记","depth":2,"text":"游记","children":[{"id":"计划参考","depth":3,"text":"计划参考"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:china:fujian:xiamen.md","_source":"content","_file":"china/fujian/xiamen.md","_extension":"md"}